                edit various config files in /usr/local/etc/laptop-mode to your liking
                $ sudo /usr/local/etc/init.d/acpid start
                $ sudo /usr/local/etc/init.d/laptop-mode status
                ..check things look as expected
                $ sudo /usr/local/etc/init.d/laptop-mode start
